:

1. *Uhvati* me za ruku! (Catch me by the hand!)
2. *Uhvatila* je priliku da ode ranije. (She seized the opportunity to leave earlier.)
3. On je *uhvatio* plijen. (He caught the prey.)
4. Ona je *uhvatila* nož pre nego što je pala. (She caught the knife before she fell.)
5. *Uhvatili* su ga. (They caught him.)